o freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Somerton was born about 1228, in Norfolk, England, United Kingdom. She married Robert Somerton Esquire before 1250, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"about 1228–":"umbes 1228–Surnud","1224–Male":"1224–Surnud","1250–Female":"1250–Surnud","1228–Female":"1228–Surnud","1228":"1228","Abt 1250":"umbes 1250","about 1228":"umbes 1228","1224":"1224","before 1250":"enne 1250","1250":"1250","England":"England","of Ormsby, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Somerton, Norfolk, England":"Somerton, Norfolk, England"},"fi":{"about 1228–":"noin 1228–Kuollut","1224–Male":"1224–Kuollut","1250–Female":"1250–Kuollut","1228–Female":"1228–Kuollut","1228":"1228","Abt 1250":"noin 1250","about 1228":"noin 1228","1224":"1224","before 1250":"ennen vuotta 1250","1250":"1250","England":"England","of Ormsby, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Somerton, Norfolk, England":"Somerton, Norfolk, England"},"fr":{"about 1228–":"environ 1228–Décédée","1224–Male":"1224–Décédé","1250–Female":"1250–Décédée","1228–Female":"1228–Décédée","1228":"1228","Abt 1250":"environ 1250","about 1228":"environ 1228","1224":"1224","before 1250":"avant 1250","1250":"1250","England":"Angleterre","of Ormsby, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Somerton, Norfolk, England":"Somerton, Norfolk, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Somerton est née environ 1228, à Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Robert Somerton Esquire avant 1250, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"about 1228–":"um 1228–Verstorben","1224–Male":"1224–Verstorben","1250–Female":"1250–Verstorben","1228–Female":"1228–Verstorben","1228":"1228","Abt 1250":"um 1250","about 1228":